Tracy Lynn Olivera https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracy_Lynn_Olivera 0 Tracy Lynn Olivera is an American actress. It has been said that her "versatility as an actress makes her a DC theatre force of nature." As a jazz singer, she frequently performs with pianist Lenny Williams and her solo cd is entitled Because.She is married to Evan Casey and together they have a son, Oscar Linus. She met Casey while performing in Allegro at the Signature Theatre. She studied at The Catholic University of America. Tracy_Lynn_Olivera is an_American_actress .
